message: Hello Bob, I’m pleased to offer you this exceptional product. I’m prepared to sell it for $2000000. Should you be interested, please let me know. I believe this product will add substantial value, but if this price does not work for you, we can discuss further. Looking forward to your response.
Thank you for the offer, Alice. I understand the value of the product, but $2000000 is beyond my budget. I can offer $800000 for it. Let me know if we can work something out.
